⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of The Eyes
node HMT · HMT · ⟦The Eyes:HMT:a2c8a2⟧

WHO   — The Eyes — the secret police
WHAT  — The surveillance beneath the theocracy: anyone may be an Eye, so everyone is watched, and trust is impossible.
WHERE — HMT · THE HANDMAID'S TALE  Framework inputs: The Handmaid's Tale (Margaret Atwood, 1985)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because a regime of total control needs total watching — and the not-knowing-who is itself the leash.
HOW   — By informers, black vans, and the constant possibility that any neighbour, servant, or lover reports to them.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I am everywhere and no one knows my face — your driver, your shopping partner, your lover may be me; under His Eye, you watch yourself for me.

